---
layout: layouts/home.njk
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Home
  order: 1
numberOfLatestPostsToShow: 3
---
{% set postsCount = collections.posts | length %}
{% set latestPostsCount = postsCount | min(numberOfLatestPostsToShow) %}
{% set postslist = collections.posts | head(-1 * numberOfLatestPostsToShow) %}
{% set postslistCounter = postsCount %}
{% set morePosts = postsCount - numberOfLatestPostsToShow %}

<section class="showcase-hero">
	<div class="showcase-hero__content">
		<p class="showcase-eyebrow">Community AI Vibe</p>
		<h1 class="showcase-hero__title">Build With AI showcases collaborative experiments and coding energy.</h1>
		<p class="showcase-hero__lede">We’re a grassroots collective shipping open builds, sharing prompts, and remixing ideas across Malaysia and beyond. Explore what the community is crafting with Eleventy, Cloudflare, and generous splashes of neon imagination.</p>
		<div class="showcase-hero__cta">
			<a class="showcase-button showcase-button--primary" href="/blog/">Browse latest drops</a>
			<a class="showcase-button showcase-button--ghost" href="/about/">Learn about BWAI</a>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="showcase-hero__visual" aria-hidden="true">
		<div class="showcase-orbit">
			<div class="showcase-orbit__ring"></div>
			<div class="showcase-orbit__ring"></div>
			<div class="showcase-orbit__ring"></div>
			<div class="showcase-orbit__node" style="top: 12%; left: 32%;" data-label="Eleventy"></div>
			<div class="showcase-orbit__node" style="bottom: 18%; right: 28%;" data-label="Cloudflare"></div>
			<div class="showcase-orbit__node" style="top: 48%; right: 8%;" data-label="Page-CMS"></div>
			<div class="showcase-orbit__core"><span>BWAI</span></div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="showcase-section showcase-section--condensed">
	<header class="showcase-section__header">
		<p class="showcase-section__eyebrow">Why this stack</p>
		<h2 class="showcase-section__title">Optimised for fast drops, community edits, and dazzling performance.</h2>
		<p class="showcase-section__lede">Eleventy powers our markdown-first workflow, Page-CMS keeps contributors in flow, and Cloudflare Pages ships updates at hyperspeed.</p>
	</header>
	<div class="showcase-feature-grid">
		<article class="showcase-feature-card">
			<h3>Eleventy + Markdown</h3>
			<p>Accessible static tooling that lets contributors focus on ideas while the generator handles structure, data, and templating flexibility.</p>
			<p class="showcase-feature-meta">Lightning builds · Flexible collections</p>
		</article>
		<article class="showcase-feature-card">
			<h3>Page-CMS integration</h3>
			<p>Editors drop content cubes straight into the pipeline—no git anxiety required. Draft toggles and custom fields keep experiments organised.</p>
			<p class="showcase-feature-meta">Human friendly · Editor ready</p>
		</article>
		<article class="showcase-feature-card">
			<h3>Cloudflare Pages</h3>
			<p>Global edge deployment with zero-config CI. Each neon launch brings responsive images, feeds, and sitemap updates automatically.</p>
			<p class="showcase-feature-meta">Worldwide · Instant rollbacks</p>
		</article>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="showcase-section">
	<header class="showcase-section__header">
		<p class="showcase-section__eyebrow">Latest drops</p>
		<h2 class="showcase-section__title">Fresh posts from the BWAI lab.</h2>
		<p class="showcase-section__lede">Catch the most recent {{ latestPostsCount }} release{% if latestPostsCount != 1 %}s{% endif %}, hand-coded and neon charged by the community.</p>
	</header>

	<div class="showcase-posts">
		{% include "postslist.njk" %}
		{% if morePosts > 0 %}
		<p class="showcase-more">{{ morePosts }} more post{% if morePosts != 1 %}s{% endif %} await in <a href="/blog/">the archive</a>.</p>
		{% endif %}
	</div>
</section>

<section class="showcase-section">
	<header class="showcase-section__header">
		<p class="showcase-section__eyebrow">Inside the build</p>
		<h2 class="showcase-section__title">Architecture, creation flow, and upgrade beacons.</h2>
		<p class="showcase-section__lede">Peek into how the platform stays modular yet community-proud, from content architecture to future enhancements.</p>
	</header>

	<div class="showcase-grid--two">
		<article class="showcase-card">
			<h3>Architecture overview</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Content lives in <code>content/</code>, layouts reside in <code>_includes/</code>, and shared data flows through <code>_data/</code>.</li>
				<li>Responsive image optimisation, navigation plugin, and RSS feeds run out of the box.</li>
				<li>Draft workflow keeps in-progress pieces out of production builds until they’re ready to glow.</li>
			</ul>
		</article>
		<article class="showcase-card">
			<h3>Creation pipeline</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Collaborators ideate scenes, capture prompts, and slot entries via Page-CMS.</li>
				<li>Eleventy regenerates the showcase, Cloudflare Pages launches the update globally.</li>
				<li>Analytics and accessibility checks ensure each drop levels up community impact.</li>
			</ul>
		</article>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="showcase-section">
	<header class="showcase-section__header">
		<p class="showcase-section__eyebrow">Roadmap highlights</p>
		<h2 class="showcase-section__title">Beaconing what’s next.</h2>
		<p class="showcase-section__lede">We’re charting new territory with analytics, internationalisation, and richer author experiences.</p>
	</header>
	<div class="showcase-roadmap">
		<ul class="showcase-roadmap__list">
			<li class="showcase-roadmap__item">
				<strong>Cloudflare analytics pulse</strong>
				<span>Activate privacy-friendly insights to measure how far the neon reaches.</span>
			</li>
			<li class="showcase-roadmap__item">
				<strong>Expanded CMS models</strong>
				<span>Launch author spotlights, build series templates, and community project submission flows.</span>
			</li>
			<li class="showcase-roadmap__item">
				<strong>Internationalisation</strong>
				<span>Prototype multilingual content paths so every voice can join the chorus.</span>
			</li>
			<li class="showcase-roadmap__item">
				<strong>Security & CSP enhancements</strong>
				<span>Introduce tighter policies while keeping bundled assets smooth.</span>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="showcase-cta">
	<h2>Bring your neon idea to life with BWAI.</h2>
	<p>Whether you’re scripting a prompt, designing a vibe-heavy illustration, or deploying a showcase app, we want you in the mix. Drop your concept and let’s build it together.</p>
	<div class="showcase-cta__actions">
		<a class="showcase-button showcase-button--primary" href="https://discord.gg/">Join the community</a>
		<a class="showcase-button showcase-button--ghost" href="/blog/">Read the archive</a>
	</div>
</section>

